ill learn. Dont depend on poison or your weapon procs or anything like that, only thing you can depend on is your backstab button, it will win you the duel if you use it right, ask a friend of yours to help you practice, learn how to beat them loosing less hp every time... duel alot of people, everyone has a diff way to duel, learn those moves and think what you can do to beat your target. <br><br>Best experience you can get is from dueling yourself, reading what other people think will not help you that much. <br><br><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=162609">Veteran Keliur T'Soul</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/Keliur/fullsize/My+wins.jpg">Ec'I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukeliur.showPublicProfile?language=EN>K e l i u r</A> at: 7/17/02 10:06:49 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukinthaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kinthaf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/17/02 12:23:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=695.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> practice..</span><hr size=1> Practicing against some friends will do you more good than anything else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umethodsz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Method SZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/2/02 2:18:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.